<p><strong>Looking down, the squares sit on 4 corners — the loop turns right, forward, left, back, then repeats, climbing each time.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Modify challenge.</strong> Change <strong>one</strong> thing and <strong>predict before you run</strong> — for example <code>range(12)</code> → <code>range(20)</code> (taller), or the turn step <code>+ 4</code> → <code>+ 6</code> (wider). Write what will change, then build it.</p>
